lds/businesses participating in energy efficiency programs\n* Capacity of community solar installations\n\n\n\n**III. Phase 3: Systemic Change & Decarbonization (Years 6-10) - "Transforming the City"**\n\n**Goal:**  Drive deeper emission reductions through systemic changes and long-term investments.\n\n**Actions:**\n\n* **Building Decarbonization (Economic & Political):**\n    * **Building Codes:**  Adopt', 'input_tokens': 27, 'output_tokens': 721, 'cost': 0.0007398999999999999, 'time_taken': 19.520814418792725}
